description: Number of 7x7 binary matrices with n ones, with no zero rows or columns, up to row and column permutation.
formula: G.f. : Z(S_7 X S_7; x_1, x_2, ...)-2*Z(S_7 X S_6; x_1, x_2, ...)+Z(S_6 X S_6; x_1, x_2, ...) if we replace x_i by 1+x^i, where Z(S_i X S_j; x_1, x_2, ...) is cycle index of Cartesian product of symmetric groups S_i and S_j of degree i and j, respectively.
author: _Vladeta Jovovic_, Aug 04 2000
